About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War," was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. The recent release Pathaan (2023) starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham is the fourth instalment in the spy universe franchise.

All the films of the Spy Universe are blockbusters with Pathaan being the all-time highest grossing Hindi film ever. The YRF Spy Universe is now one of the biggest IP‚Äôs in the history of Indian cinema. The next film from this franchise is Tiger 3 releasing this Diwali!

YRF Spy Universe films boast of incredible visual spectacles with high-octane action sequences, thrilling plot-lines, power-packed characters and musical chartbusters.

Adda247, India's largest vernacular Exam preparation company founded in 2010. Adda247 provides well curated course content & teaching by top faculties of industry for all types of Exam preparations, i.e., Govt jobs, IIT, Medical, State Exams, etc.

Rate Us On IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt29424187/

Kisi bhi ladai mein insaan ki aadhi jeet tabhi ho jati hai jab vo ladne ki himmat juta le. Student Shiv ko uske papa ne ghar se nikaal diya hai aur ab vo aa gaya hai Mukherjee Nagar ke warzone mein, jahan sapne bante bhi hai aur bigadte bhi. Dosari taraf SSC sir ke best teacher ko Khanna hijack kar leta hai aur us par ilzaam bhi lagata hai. Nayi nayi problems sar utha rahi hain lekin hope ki ungali thame Shiv aur SSC badh rahe hain kadam dar kadam.

snippet.title: Every Indian Mom | Ft. Tena Jaiin | The Paayal Jain
snippet.description:
Hey Guys ,
This video shows different behavious of Every Indian Mom . This is a very comic and relatable video . Mom packing birthday gift for neighbour 's child . Packing birthday gift and giving multiple instructions to behave properly in family gatherings with relatives . 90's style cake , samosa , dhokla chips . Indian Mom always convincing daughter to get married and not to be too choosy for the right guy for being husband . Boys , sundays and cricket matches . Chintu on the early sunday morning trying to sneakout to play bat ball with his friends . Savitri being the strict mom , took him to sabzi mandi . Navratri and durga maa pooja , navratri Fast food , Navratri vrat khana , bhabhi making everything for nanad and beti feeding them with hindu fast food , sabudana , kuttu , makhana , aloo , samak and avoiding onion , garlic Fasting all 9 days then preparing for kanjak . Guests coming suddendly with Ramleela Vip passes watching ram sita hanuman and excitment of going to dussehra mela ravan . Moms bragging about how modern they are and they give so much freedom to their kids , on the contrary daughter is having flashbacks of how her mom so strict . Mom waking childern on sunday despite everyone's holiday , she works all the days of the week cooking fresh breakfast , aloo ke parathe , watching them eat makes her happy and she sacrifices her own food for the love of her child . Moms when gives threat to leave the house , goes sit in the stairs , then in mandir , whole indian family goes out searching for maa , daughter crying for mom , she comes back . Maa Vs beti . Maa Beti during school picnic , school holiday homework . school exams , those exam days hiding answer sheets from her , moms during holi ,  Indian parents about privacy and using facebook , instagram social media , comparing their kids with other topper kids , not ever satisfied with their excellence , warning daughter about sex when she enters her college life , daughter and her first period , freaking out on periods , over feeding beti and then blaming her for being over weight bubbly child and not letting do dieting , surprising mom on her birthday with gift and cake mother gets shocked and scolds her for wasting money , never happy , Mothers and their millions of excuses when it comes to exercising or changing life. Mummy shouting , gossiping, watching serials and many more crazy situations. Still our mothers love us and we love our mother so much
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part,

This video shows different behavious of Every Indian Mom . This is a very comic and relatable video . Mom packing birthday gift for neighbour 's child . Packing birthday gift and giving multiple instructions to behave properly in family gatherings with relatives . 90's style cake , samosa , dhokla chips . Indian Mom always convincing daughter to get married and not to be too choosy for the right guy for being husband . Boys , sundays and cricket matches . Chintu on the early sunday morning trying to sneakout to play bat ball with his friends . Savitri being the strict mom , took him to sabzi mandi . Navratri and durga maa pooja , navratri Fast food , Navratri vrat khana , bhabhi making everything for nanad and beti feeding them with hindu fast food , sabudana , kuttu , makhana , aloo , samak and avoiding onion , garlic Fasting all 9 days then preparing for kanjak . Guests coming suddendly with Ramleela Vip passes watching ram sita hanuman and excitment of going to dussehra mela ravan . Moms bragging about how modern they are and they give so much freedom to their kids , on the contrary daughter is having flashbacks of how her mom so strict . Mom waking childern on sunday despite everyone's holiday , she works all the days of the week cooking fresh breakfast , aloo ke parathe , watching them eat makes her happy and she sacrifices her own food for the love of her child . Moms when gives threat to leave the house , goes sit in the stairs , then in mandir , whole indian family goes out searching for maa , daughter crying for mom , she comes back . Maa Vs beti . Maa Beti during school picnic , school holiday homework . school exams , those exam days hiding answer sheets from her , moms during holi ,  Indian parents about privacy and using facebook , instagram social media , comparing their kids with other topper kids , not ever satisfied with their excellence , warning daughter about sex when she enters her college life , daughter and her first period , freaking out on periods , over feeding beti and then blaming her for being over weight bubbly child and not letting do dieting , surprising mom on her birthday with gift and cake mother gets shocked and scolds her for wasting money , never happy , Mothers and their millions of excuses when it comes to exercising or changing life. Mummy shouting , gossiping, watching serials and many more crazy situations. Still our mothers love us and we love our mother so much
Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia
Do share it with your friends and family especially guests .. Comment down your Fav Part,

snippet.title: Ghost | Second OGM | Dr.Shivarajkumar | Anupam Kher | Jayaram | Prashant Narayanan | Sandesh | Srini
snippet.description:
This action packed heist thriller, directed by Srini, tells the story of one man's quest for justice. This apart the film offers a link to the second installment of "Birbal Trilogy", the director's awaited legal thriller. Powerhouse talents such as Dr Shivarajkumar, Anupam Kher, Jayaram, Prashanth Narayan, Archana Jois, Satyaprakash and Dattanna are part of the film's main cast.
Arjun Jaya's striking background scores and cinematographer Mahendra Simha's captivating visuals promise to take the film a notch higher.
We now welcome you to the world of #GHOST. See you in the cinemas this Dasara.

On the fourth day of Navratri 2023, devotees worship Kushmanda Mata, and sing her aarti. Kushmanda Mata is believed to bless her devotees with good health, success, and prosperity. The aarti glorifies her strength and divinity, and seeks her blessings for happiness and peace. Devotees perform puja and offer flowers, fruits, and sweets to the deity. The festive mood resonates in the air as people come together to celebrate the auspicious occasion.

Language - Hindi
Album - Soulful Mantras Bhajans Vol 4
Artist - leena bose & aditya jayant ankam

snippet.title: The Mona Lisa Mystery | Why is it World's Most Famous Painting? | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
Compare & Book Fixed Deposits with Stable Money, Download app : https://stablemoney.app.link/gUbgNjY2DDb

In this video, Dhruv Rathee dives deep into the captivating tale of the Mona Lisa. Set in the bustling city of Paris, an audacious theft occurs at the Louvre Museum. The mastermind, Vincenzo Peruggia, along with accomplices Michele Lancelotti and Vincenzo, manage to steal Leonardo da Vinci's iconic painting, the Mona Lisa. Astonishingly, the theft has remained unnoticed for nearly 30 hours. Eventually, the world is alerted to the crime, and even the legendary artist Pablo Picasso is questioned! The painting remains missing for 16 months, and its return to the Louvre only adds to its global fame. We then delve into the woman's identity depicted in the painting, Lisa Gherardini, and the various theories surrounding her. The painting's artistic traits, the science behind Mona Lisa's elusive smile, and the discovery of another possible version of the painting are also discussed. Join us as we unravel the mysteries behind one of the world's most celebrated artworks and its intriguing history.

snippet.title: MANDI BIRYANI | 3 Full Goat Arabian Mutton Mandi Recipe Cooking In Village | Kuzhi Mandhi Biryani
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook mutton mandi recipe by cooking three full goats. Kuzhi Mandi recipe is one of the famous Arabian food which is cooking meat and rice together in underground. We do the same traditional Arabian method to get the real taste of the mandi Recipe.

 We tasted Mutton Mandhi for the first time in our life! Really Tasty!

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3904: Chai Ne Bigadi Deal
--------------------------------------------------------
Vicky, one of Jethalal's clients, is upset and insults him after Jethalal unintentionally spills his tea on him. Vicky also accuses him of revenge after Jetha refuses to deal with him after Vicky disagrees to give advanced money for the deal. Babita talks about Jetha to his friend who is looking for a dealer for a big order. Jethalal later learns that Vicky is the husband of Babita's acquaintance and is shocked. Watch the episode

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3904, 17 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3903 | 16 Oct 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3903: Babita Ki Dost
--------------------------------------------------------
Jethalal finally wakes up early and leaves for work, but on the way, he clashes with Champaklal, and Champaklal falls down. Jetha tells Champaklal that he was caught reading his phone's text messages, so he didn't notice him coming. Champaklal taunts Jetha, saying that he was also reading his newspaper and was engrossed in it. Later, Popatlal gets happy when he sees that Babita has a special visitor. He escorts her to Babita's house, postponing his work. Who is Babita's companion Popatlal taking an interest in?

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3903, 16 Oct 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Date With A A.I | Ft. Anushka Kaushik & Ritik Ghanshani | RVCJ Media
snippet.description:
India's largest news network, India Today Group, introduced the country's first artificial intelligence news anchor Sana in March 2023. AI anchor Sana launched at the 20th edition of India Today Conclave. India Today Group has introduced many bot AI collaborative anchors with the help of modern technology. These anchors are not only ageless and never tired, but are also proficient in speaking many languages.

Subscribe to Aaj Tak AI YouTube Channel:   
https://www.youtube.com/@aajtakai
Visit Aaj Tak website: https://www.aajtak.in/topic/ai-anchors
Follow Aaj Tak on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/aianchorsana

Step into a future where technology rules, but love transcends it all.   
In the year 2042, follow Ankuj, a young man who despises the virtual world, where connections are made through screens, not hearts.  His scientist father, Dr. Avinash Kulkarni, living on Mars, leaves him feeling abandoned on his birthday.
A mysterious gift, "Project Rachna," from his father changes everything. Through futuristic glasses, Ankush is reunited with his late mother, Rachana, thanks to his father's creation.
Witness the power of memories, love and the irreplaceable bond between a mother and her child.

Join us on this journey where technology meets emotion and where 'A.A.I (‡§Ü‡§à)' represents the smartest and most emotionally intelligent creation, ever to exist. 

For more updates, stay connected with us: 
See us on Instagram:  https://www.instagram.com/rvcjinsta/?...
Like us on Facebook: https://fb.com/TheRVCJMedia‚Äã‚Äã‚Äã‚Äã‚Äã‚Äã

snippet.description:
This one is super special!
Noori is all about those unforgettable memories and that one-of-a-kind love that can't be duplicated by anyone else.
Y‚Äôall killed it with the teaser, so show as much and more support for the song!
Let me know your favourite part in the comments below.

Lyrics :
Tenu karan yaad inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda
Tenu karan pyaar inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda
 
tu meriyan ve saari gallan janda
mai tetho sanga sab tu pehchhanda
Way sarda na hove jado dur tu
haal ankhan vicho padh mutiyaar da
 
tera jeya sachi ve koi sohna ni
ae kehn da tareeka koi hona ni
paleya mai tenu kade khone ni
Mai vi karan tenu pyar
 
Mai kol tere v awa
Te naal tenu bithawa
Je pyar kara madi tenu
Te pyar hi mai v chawa
Karan kadar tere mai pyar di
Tan hi khushi tenu din raat dava
Mai na hor kise de naal dissa
Bas tenu hi mai chawa
 
Tenu rakha way mai dil ch wassa k
Noor way bna k zindagi tu meriye
Teri ankh wich surmaa mai paa k
Kol way bitha k karan gallan teriyeee
 
Tenu karan yaad inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda
Tenu karan pyaar inhaa jinaa koi kar nahi sakda

Mannat Murad Episode 07 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 17th October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?

snippet.title: Tata Safari 2023 Facelift Drive Impressions | Gagan Choudhary
snippet.description:
Namaste, I got a chance to drive the new facelifted Tata Safari recently, which now comes with a lot of updates both on exteriors and interiors. This was obviously a diesel version as Safari is not available with a Petrol engine yet. Please find out all my Impressions in the video and refer to these timestamps if you need them.

00:00 Introduction
00:26 Exteriors including DRLs, Front bumper, Key Fob features, Wheels, Tyres, Headlights, Taillights, Rear, etc
02:39 Boots Space and Toolkit
05:52 Interiors including MID, Infotainment, Steering, AC, Seats, Sunroof, Center console, gear knob, etc
14:40 Rear Seat Space, Amenities, Comfort etc
17:05 Last-row or third-row seat comfort, Space and amenities
18:37 Drive Impressions including Ride Quality, Handling, Engine, Gearbox, Braking, etc
23:30 Tata Harrier/Safari Off-Road Modes
25:40 Conclusion

snippet.title: SSC | EP 01: First Attempt | Amit Bhadana
snippet.description:
Download Adda247 App: https://adda247.app.link/Amit_Bhadana_E1

Adda247, India's largest vernacular Exam preparation company founded in 2010. Adda247 provides well curated course content & teaching by top faculties of industry for all types of Exam preparations, i.e., Govt jobs, IIT, Medical, State Exams, etc.

Rate Us On IMDB: https://www.imdb.com/title/tt29424187/

SSC, vo exam jo lakhon students ki umeed hai aur kuch logon ke liye profitable business. Ye kahani hai SSC yani Shiv Shankar Chaudhary aur uski life ke 2 important phases ki. Ek hai graduation ke samay Shiv jise SSC crack karne se jyada tension rehti hai apne papa ke gusse ki. Dosara Shiv Delhi NCR ka upcoming SSC training institute chalata hai aur apne rival Khanna ke plans ka shikar hota rehta hai. Aieye dekhte hain kya hai in dono ka struggle?

Episode 3886: Kharab Speaker
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha is taken aback when he sees Bagha, and Nattu Kaka has posted a special notice about the "Mega Sale" at the store. Bagha explains to Jetha why such a declaration was made. He and Nattu Kaka have devised a strategy for the store's stock removal. Finally, Jetha expresses relief and commends them on their profitable concept. Meanwhile, Bhide presents Madhvi with a beautiful saree for Ganesh Chaturthi. Sonu becomes moved after witnessing Bhide and Madhvi's adorable moment. Later, when Tapu arrives to meet Sonu, Bhide is dissatisfied.

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - promotes 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), a Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Nitish Bhaluni). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

Mannat Murad Episode 06 - [Eng Sub] - Iqra Aziz - Talha Chahour - Digitally Presented by PEL - 16th October 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Mannat Murad Digitally Presented by PEL

Mannat is a beautiful young girl who hails from a progressive family that values love, care, and mutual respect. Raised in an environment where everyone's choices are respected, Mannat enjoys the freedom to make her own decisions. Following the untimely demise of her parents, she finds support from her elder brother, Nafees, who showers her with affection.

On the other hand, Murad belongs to a conservative family where his mother, the matriarch, wields significant influence over his life choices. As the only son, Murad is burdened with the responsibility of fulfilling his family's expectations. Soft-spoken and romantic by nature, Murad finds himself unable to defy his mother's authority, especially after the passing of his father.

Despite their starkly contrasting backgrounds, Mannat and Murad's hearts find solace in each other's presence, and they fall deeply in love. However, their families' interference creates misunderstandings between Mannat and Murad, testing the strength of their bond.

Will their families agree to their union? Will Mannat's family, with their open-mindedness, find common ground with Murad's conservative household? Can Mannat and Murad's love for each other withstand the motives of their families, who seek to create further misunderstandings between them?
